{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/startusing"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Шаг 1. Получите API-ключ для MapsNativeSDK","level":2,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-1-%D0%9F%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%83%D1%87%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B5-API-%D0%BA%D0%BB%D1%8E%D1%87-%D0%B4%D0%BB%D1%8F-MapsNativeSDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Подробнее о вариантах получения ключа читайте на "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/dev.vk.com\/ru\/vkmaps\/general-information\/api-key"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Шаг 2. Подключите MapsNativeSDK к проекту","level":2,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-2-%D0%9F%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BA%D0%BB%D1%8E%D1%87%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B5-MapsNativeSDK-%D0%BA-%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B5%D0%BA%D1%82%D1%83"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"В данный момент MapsNativeSDK распространяется с помощью архива с несколькими "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".xcframework"},{"type":"text","text":"-пакетами."}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Откройте свой проект с помощью Xcode.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Выберите необходимый target, в котором будут использоваться возможности SDK.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Во вкладке General добавьте все предоставленные ","type":"text"},{"code":".xcframework","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"-файлы в раздел ","type":"text"},{"code":"Frameworks, Libraries, and Embedded Content","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". На скриншоте ниже показан пример добавленных фреймворков в target.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"addedFrameworks"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Шаг 3. Используйте MapsNativeSDK","level":2,"anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-3-%D0%98%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D1%83%D0%B9%D1%82%D0%B5-MapsNativeSDK"},{"type":"heading","text":"Импорт SDK","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%98%D0%BC%D0%BF%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%82-SDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Импортируйте "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapsNativeSDK"},{"type":"text","text":" в файл, в котором вы будете использовать карту."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import MapsNativeSDK"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Конфигурация SDK","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%86%D0%B8%D1%8F-SDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Сконфигурируйте SDK, используя метод "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapsSDKConfigurator\/setup(baseURL:apiKey:diskCachePath:maxCacheSizeBytes:fileTimeoutSec:)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Конфигурация с передачей только API-ключа","MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: ##API-ключ##)","","\/\/ Конфигурация с передачей дополнительных параметров","MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(baseURL: ##Базовый URL для загрузки тайлов и предустановленных стиле##,","                          apiKey: ##API-ключ##,","                          diskCachePath: ##Путь для хранения файлов кэша на диске##,","                          maxCacheSizeBytes: ##Максимальный размер файлового кэша в байтах##,","                          fileTimeoutSec: ## Время жизни файлов в кэше ###)"]},{"type":"aside","style":"important","name":"Important","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Если не указать путь к файловому кэшу, то SDK не будет кешировать данные в виде файлов.","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Конфигурация карты","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%86%D0%B8%D1%8F-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D1%8B"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Создайте конфигурацию для карты с помощью типа "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapConfiguration"},{"type":"text","text":", указав исходные настройки карты."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Кофигурация для карты с использованием предустановленного стиля","let configuration = MapConfiguration(","    center: ##Стартовые координаты центра карты##,","    zoom: ##Стартовый зум карты##,","    predefinedStyle: .simple",")"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Вместо предустановленных стилей вы можете передать стиль, загруженный с помощью типа "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapStyle"},{"type":"text","text":" или строку в формате JSON (подробнее в статье "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Styles"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Создание делегата","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%A1%D0%BE%D0%B7%D0%B4%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%B3%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B0"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Вам необходимо создать объект-делегат карты, в котором в дальнейшем вы сможете обрабатывать события жизненного цикла карты (подробнее в статье "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Lifecycle"},{"type":"text","text":"). При создании делегата подпишитесь на протокол "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapViewDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Определение класса-делегата","class BaseMapViewDelegate: MapViewDelegate {}","","\/\/ ...","","\/\/ Создание делегата","let delegate = BaseMapViewDelegate()"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"В дальнейшем данный объект потребуется передать при создании экземпляра типа "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Не требуется реализовывать методы ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapViewDelegate"},{"text":", если их функциональность вам не нужна.","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Размещение карт на экране","level":3,"anchor":"%D0%A0%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82-%D0%BD%D0%B0-%D1%8D%D0%BA%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B5"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNativeSDK могут быть использованы в приложениях, основанных на UIKit и SwiftUI. Далее рассмотрим каждую из платформ."}]},{"type":"aside","style":"warning","name":"Warning","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Убедитесь, что к этому моменту вы сконфигурировали SDK с помощью вызова ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapsSDKConfigurator.setup"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Использование в UIKit-проекте","level":4,"anchor":"%D0%98%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%B2-UIKit-%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B5%D0%BA%D1%82%D0%B5"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Для использования карты в UIKit необходимо создать объект "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView"},{"type":"text","text":", передав в него конфигурацию, и разместить созданный объект на экране."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class ViewController: UIViewController {","","    override func viewDidLoad() {","        super.viewDidLoad()","        \/\/ Конфигурирование SDK","        MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: \"...\")","        \/\/ Создание конфигурации карты","        let configuration = MapConfiguration(center: Coordinates(lng: 37.6156, lat: 55.7522), zoom: 10, predefinedStyle: .main)","        \/\/ Создание объекта карты","        let mapView = MapView(frame: CGRect(x: 0, y: 0,","                                            width: UIScreen.main.bounds.width,","                                            height: UIScreen.main.bounds.height),","                              configuration: configuration,","                              delegate: self)","        \/\/ Размещение карты на экране","        view.addSubview(mapView)","    }","}","","\/\/ Делегат карты","extension ViewController: MapViewDelegate {}"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Использование в SwiftUI-проекте","level":4,"anchor":"%D0%98%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%B2-SwiftUI-%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B5%D0%BA%D1%82%D0%B5"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Для использования карты в SwiftUI необходимо создать объект ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" и передать его в структуру ","type":"text"},{"code":"Map","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"code":["\/\/ Делегат для MapView","class BaseMapViewDelegate: MapViewDelegate {}","","\/\/ View-модель экрана, где будет использоваться карта","final class ContentViewModel: ObservableObject {","    \/\/ Объект карты","    let mapView: MapView","    \/\/ Объект делегата карты","    private let mapViewDelegate: MapViewDelegate","    ","    init() {","        \/\/ Конфигурирование SDK","        MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: \"...\")","        \/\/ Создание конфигурации карты","        let configuration = MapConfiguration(center: Coordinates(lng: 37.6156, lat: 55.7522), zoom: 10, predefinedStyle: .main)","        \/\/ Создание делегата карты","        let delegate = BaseMapViewDelegate()","        mapViewDelegate = delegate","        \/\/ Создание объекта карты","        mapView = MapView(configuration: configuration, delegate: delegate)","    }","}","","\/\/ Экран с картой","struct ContentView: View {","    @StateObject private var viewModel = ContentViewModel()","","    var body: some View {","        Map(view: viewModel.mapView)","            .frame(maxWidth: .infinity, maxHeight: .infinity)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Интегрируйте карты в свое приложение на основе UIKit или SwiftUI."}],"kind":"article","sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"MapsNativeSDK"}],"role":"article","title":"Начало работы с MapsNativeSDK"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/StartUsing"},"references":{"addedFrameworks":{"type":"image","identifier":"addedFrameworks","alt":"Added frameworks","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/MapsNativeSDK\/addedFrameworks.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK/MapView":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MapView","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/mapview","abstract":[{"text":"Main object of the Map","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MapView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView"},"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK/Lifecycle":{"title":"Отслеживание событий карты","type":"topic","role":"article","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/mapsnativesdk\/lifecycle","abstract":[{"text":"Отслеживайте события, происходящие с картой, и программируйте реакцию на них.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Lifecycle"},"doc://MapsNativeSDK/documentation/MapsNativeSDK/MapConfiguration":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MapConfiguration